title: At New York's Trump Tower, condo prices have lost their glitter
text:
At New York's Trump Tower, condo prices have lost their glitter Friday, April 13, 2018 - 01:37 
President Donald Trump's gilded New York home and headquarters of his business empire is emblematic of how a high-rise that once defined luxury has lost its luster. Aleksandra Michalska reports.
